      "role": "user",
      "content": "ok so its basically just a buffer. i guess i'm just worried about the \"guarding\" part of it. like, what if the person holding the money is incompetent or just tries to hoard it? what's the actual mechanism that ensures the \"guardian\" of the funds does their job right?",
